title: 1000 mile European Road Trip - Portugal, Spain, Gibraltar & Morocco
description:
My family of five is spending Thanksgiving road tripping across Portugal, Spain, Gibraltar and Morocco in just 8 days. Its going to be a whirlwind ride of adventure for our family and we are bringing you along for the ride.
